org.lukep.javavis.metrics
Class MetricRegistry

java.lang.Object
  org.lukep.javavis.metrics.MetricRegistry

public class MetricRegistry
extends java.lang.Object

The MetricRegistry is a singleton that stores all of the MetricAttributes and cached MetricMeasurements in the program's memory.

See Also:
MetricAttribute, MetricMeasurement
